  <div id="text-content_7dfc5a00-29af-4af2-b569-4815bdeeb62c" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Edit Settings </strong>button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="set_user_time_zone" data-step-uuid="23fe1314-e4e1-43ec-af81-09581964e5a6">
    <h2 id="set_user_time_zone" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Select Pronouns</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/026/693/original/a5fe818d-1d80-4130-8182-8f7808cfe29b.png" srcset="" alt="Select Pronouns" height="608" width="523">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_1704daea-e3dc-4ec1-987f-65f81bf1ce80" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the <strong>Pronouns</strong> drop-down menu, select your personal pronouns.</p>
<p><strong>Notes:</strong> </p>
<ul>
<li>If the Pronouns drop-down menu does not display in your User Settings, your institution has not enabled this feature.</li>
<li>Pronoun options are managed by your institution. You cannot add pronoun options.</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="update_settings" data-step-uuid="1076c3a0-6bcf-4059-910a-a9384cc02a87">
