  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_50fd8d57-04f2-47d9-9356-1cff93c5054f" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Update Settings </strong>button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

